snippet.title: Kio's Adventure - Steam Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Kio's Adventure on: http://store.steampowered.com/app/612070/

"Kio's Adventure" tells the story about a high school girl named Kio suddenly goes to a different world which is surrounded by organs and monsters after a wired earthquake. Players need to help Kio escape this horrible world. The game artwork uses 16bit pixel style.

Games reviews and download: http://download.online-games.co/
